751|- **sharpest_insight**: The tension between micro and macro is at a critical juncture for BTC. The perp market structure data (67-day negative funding streak → historically 83-96% positive 90-day returns) is the most bullish structural setup since late 2022. The macro data (FOMC hawkish, BoJ hiking) is the most bearish since the Fed started cutting. These two forces are pulling in opposite directions. The resolution will determine the next significant move. If perp structure wins, BTC rallies through macro headwinds. If macro wins, the structural reset fails.
752|- **danger_of_misuse**: (1) Buying BTC based solely on the historical funding streak backtest (83-96% win rate) — this ignores the FOMC hawkish regime shift that postdates the analysis. (2) Overinterpreting the sunshine trading paper as a reason to execute all trades visibly — only applies when your trade has no private information content. (3) Using the dot-com vs AI comparison as a timing signal — the unwind could take years, not days. (4) Assuming OpenAI's losses mean the entire AI sector is unprofitable — inference economics is diverging from model training economics.
